    public abstract class Dagger1MvpViewStateActivity<V extends MvpView,P extends MvpPresenter<V>>
extends MvpViewStateActivity<V,P>
implements Injector
    A MvpViewStateActivity with dagger1 support by implementing Injector.

    Does not automatically inject itself dependencies. To do so please override MosbyActivity.injectDependencies()

      • getObjectGraph

        public ObjectGraph getObjectGraph()
        Returns daggers object graph. As default Dagger1MvpViewStateActivity assumes that your Application implements Injector and that one will be accessed. If you want to do your own thing override this method. However, injecting should not be done in this method but in MosbyActivity.injectDependencies()
        Specified by:
        getObjectGraph in interface Injector
